# In day 2 we are gona to create a tip calculator with new topic f-string and tip calculation with using of mathematical operators

print("welcome to the tip calculator!")
bill =float(input("what is the total bill? $"))
tip =int(input("What percentage tip would you like to give? 10 12 15 "))
people =int(input("how many people to split the bill? "))

tip_persentage=tip/100
tip_persentage_bill=bill*tip_persentage
total_bill=bill+tip_persentage_bill
bill_per_person = total_bill / people
print(f"each person need to pay: ${bill_per_person}")
